The following files are MODIFIED versions of files originally from vLLM and/or the
community `kyuz0/vllm-therock-gfx1151` image, redistributed here under Apache-2.0
with the modifications described below:

- pytorch_patched.py
    Original: vllm/model_executor/kernels/linear/scaled_mm/pytorch.py (vLLM, Apache-2.0)
    Modification: route FP8 (W8A8) matmuls to the custom Triton dequant-GEMV in
    fp8_triton.py instead of torch._scaled_mm (which is unsupported on RDNA/gfx1151).

- rocm_patched.py
    Original: vllm/platforms/rocm.py (vLLM, Apache-2.0; the APU VRAM workaround
    block originates from the kyuz0/vllm-therock-gfx1151 image).
    Modification: _patched_mem_info reads BOTH mem_info_vram_total and
    mem_info_gtt_total and uses max(...), so the dedicated-VRAM BIOS layout reports
    the full pool (the stock patch read GTT only and broke that layout).

fp8_triton.py and the scripts under bench/ are original work.
